marketing: Shell Rotella ET Grease is a lithium complex grease based on high viscous mineral oils for extra retention on exposed surfaces such as fifth wheel plates, springs, trailers, open pivot joints and weather exposed equipment. It contains anti-oxidants, EP-and wear preventive additives and rust inhibitors for long service life and corrosion protection.
